---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import RelatedPosts from "../components/RelatedPosts.astro";

const metaTitle = "Exploring Different Types of Swivel Seat Mechanisms";
const metaDescription =
  "Manual, powered, and memory swivel seat mechanisms—how they work, ease of use, and who they suit best.";
const currentSlug = "exploring-different-types-of-swivel-seat-mechanisms";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith("/") ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
const ogImage = `${base}logo.png`;
---

<BaseLayout title={metaTitle} description={metaDescription} headerVariant="solid">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta property="og:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={ogImage} />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={ogImage} />
  </Fragment>

  <article class="article">
    <header class="article-head">
      <p class="article-date">June 19, 2023 · by vivek</p>
      <h1>Exploring Different Types of Swivel Seat Mechanisms</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="article-grid">
      <div class="article-body">
        <h2>Manual Swivel Seat Mechanisms</h2>
        <p>
          Manual swivel seat mechanisms are the most basic type of swivel seat mechanism. They are operated by hand, using
          a lever or knob. Manual swivel seat mechanisms are typically the most affordable option, but they can be
          difficult to use, especially for people with limited mobility.
        </p>

        <h2>Powered Swivel Seat Mechanisms</h2>
        <p>
          Powered swivel seat mechanisms are operated by electricity. They are typically more expensive than manual swivel
          seat mechanisms, but they are also easier to use and offer a number of advantages. Powered swivel seat mechanisms
          can be swiveled with a button or switch, and they often have a memory function that allows the driver to save
          their preferred seating position.
        </p>

        <h2>Memory Swivel Seat Mechanisms</h2>
        <p>
          Memory swivel seat mechanisms are a type of powered swivel seat mechanism that allows the driver to save their
          preferred seating position. This can be helpful for people who share a vehicle, as they can each save their own
          seating position and have the seat automatically adjust to their preferred settings when they get in the car.
        </p>

        <h2>Conclusion</h2>
        <p>
          The type of swivel seat mechanism that is right for you will depend on your individual needs and preferences. If
          you are looking for the most affordable option, a manual swivel seat mechanism may be a good choice. If you are
          looking for a more convenient and easy-to-use option, a powered swivel seat mechanism may be a better choice. And
          if you are looking for a swivel seat mechanism that allows you to save your preferred seating position, a memory
          swivel seat mechanism may be the best option for you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar" aria-label="Products">
        <div class="products-card">
          <h2>Products</h2>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nlMO30_RrKc"
                title="TurnPlus video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus</p>
              <p class="product-link">Swivel solution for easier entry/exit.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus-electric" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ytQ7nRd8rf4"
                title="TurnPlus Electric video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus Electric</p>
              <p class="product-link">Powered swivel seat convenience.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus-accelerate" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-bSUnSfkD-8"
                title="TurnPlus Accelerate video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus Accelerate</p>
              <p class="product-link">Rapid, smooth swivel assistance.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </article>

  <RelatedPosts currentSlug={currentSlug} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .article {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .article-head h1 {
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .article-date {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .article-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .article-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #451e5d;
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0.15rem;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }

  .sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }

  .products-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 0.9rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .products-card h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.6rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    background: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    border-color: #451e5d;
  }

  .video-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #000;
  }

  .video-frame iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  .product-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .product-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-link {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .article-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
